---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-pine mb-8">About Good Christmas Ideas</h1>

    <div class="prose-custom space-y-6">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
        Finding the perfect gift shouldn't be stressful. We're here to help you discover thoughtful
        presents for everyone on your list.
      </p>

      <section>
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          Good Christmas Ideas was created with one simple goal: to make holiday gift shopping easier.
          We know how overwhelming it can be to find the right gift for the dad who has everything,
          the teen who's impossible to shop for, or the coworker you barely know.
        </p>
        <p>
          That's why we do the research so you don't have to. We spend hours reading reviews, comparing
          products, and curating lists of genuinely good gift ideas at every price point.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>How We Choose Products</h2>
        <p>Every product we recommend goes through our selection process:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Highly Rated:</strong> We look for products with strong customer reviews (typically 4+ stars)</li>
          <li><strong>Good Value:</strong> We consider quality relative to price, not just the cheapest option</li>
          <li><strong>Actually Useful:</strong> We focus on gifts people will actually use, not gimmicks</li>
          <li><strong>Available:</strong> We verify products are in stock and can ship in time</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Our Promise</h2>
        <p>
          We're committed to honest recommendations. While we do earn commissions through affiliate
          links (which helps keep this site running), we never recommend products just because they
          pay higher commissions. Our reputation depends on giving you advice you can trust.
        </p>
        <p>
          If we wouldn't give it to our own family, we won't recommend it to yours.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Beyond Christmas</h2>
        <p>
          While our name says "Christmas," great gifts are needed year-round. Our guides work just
          as well for birthdays, anniversaries, Father's Day, Mother's Day, graduations, and any
          occasion where you want to give something meaningful.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl">
        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>
          Have a question, suggestion, or feedback? We'd love to hear from you. Visit our
          <a href="/contact">Contact page</a> to reach us.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
